From d976f4569408018bf22940c7a80bb220b59ba15e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tugadane <tugas.x1@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 2026 03:55:09 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(step11+12): email notifications + complete admin panel
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Step 11 — Email notifications:
- Add 4 Mailables (OrderConfirmedMail, CommissionEarnedMail, CourseCompletedMail, WithdrawalProcessedMail) with markdown templates
- Hook OrderConfirmedMail into PaymentController@notification and Admin\\OrderController@konfirmasi after status=paid
- Hook CommissionEarnedMail into CommissionService::calculate after each commission insert
- Hook CourseCompletedMail into LearningController@markComplete on first 100% completion
- Hook WithdrawalProcessedMail into Admin\\WithdrawalController@update after approve/reject
- Schedule queue:work --stop-when-empty every minute via routes/console.php
- Add MAIL_ENCRYPTION + sensible MAIL_* defaults to .env.example

Step 12 — Admin panel:
- Admin\\DashboardController with 4 KPI cards (members, monthly revenue, monthly commission, active products), 30-day Chart.js line, 10 latest orders
- Admin\\ProductController with full CRUD, section/lesson management, SortableJS drag-drop reorder, JS slug auto-generate, thumbnail upload (jpeg/png/webp ≤2MB) renamed via Str::uuid() to storage/public/thumbnails
- Admin\\MemberController index + show (profile, referrer, downline, purchases, commissions)
- Admin\\WithdrawalController with approve/reject + admin_note + balance debit + email queue
- Admin\\ReportController with month/year filter and per-product totals row
- Sidebar updated to use new route names + add Laporan link
